Dialogue: 1,0:00:07.94,0:00:08.80,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Miyo-chan!
Dialogue: 1,0:00:10.33,0:00:11.27,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,It'll be alright.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:12.19,0:00:13.67,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,The party's starting soon.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:14.24,0:00:15.40,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:16.00,0:00:17.39,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Are you nervous?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:17.76,0:00:19.75,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I've never worn a dress before.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:20.38,0:00:22.15,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Will I even be able to walk properly in this?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.15,0:00:23.94,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 1,0:00:23.94,0:00:25.45,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,It looks great on you.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:25.45,0:00:27.63,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Plus, you studied so hard for this.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.33,0:00:32.91,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Believe in yourself, you've got this!
Dialogue: 1,0:00:35.00,0:00:37.46,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Hazuki-san.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:38.85,0:00:39.96,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,That's my girl.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.12,0:02:32.28,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,If I'm not on my best behavior...
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.80,0:02:35.03,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm going to embarass Kiyoka.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.15,0:02:37.43,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I have to do my best!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.75,0:02:46.55,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Miyo!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.70,0:02:51.65,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Kiyoka-sama.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.19,0:02:53.67,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting for me.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.98,0:02:57.91,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Um, Kiyoka-sama...
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.36,0:02:59.80,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.02,0:03:02.81,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,You're stunning.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.21,0:03:05.78,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.27,0:03:09.69,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,You look quite handsome as well.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.41,0:03:13.07,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,How forward of you.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.95,0:03:14.80,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.59,0:03:19.33,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Shall we?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.26,0:03:20.83,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.58,0:03:48.57,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Kiyoka Kudou's new fiancée is from the Saimori Clan...
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.57,0:03:52.18,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Saimori isn't a name you hear often these days.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.33,0:03:54.59,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I wonder what she's like.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.79,0:03:59.54,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,This is their first time making a public appearance together.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.08,0:04:04.23,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Is that…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.32,0:04:05.28,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.72,0:04:06.52,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.22,0:04:11.22,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I... feel like I've already made some kind of mistake.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.26,0:04:15.49,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I can feel everyone staring at me.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.03,0:04:18.51,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,You haven't made any mistakes.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.38,0:04:20.99,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Today is just a casual gathering.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.45,0:04:24.84,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,It's a chance for everyone to make their introductions.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.72,0:04:26.62,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Miyo-chan!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.32,0:04:29.55,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Hazuki-san.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.80,0:04:33.12,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Still nervous?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.07,0:04:36.11,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Your etiquette is perfect.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.24,0:04:37.57,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.01,0:04:39.57,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.78,0:04:40.86,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.77,0:04:47.89,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.26,0:04:49.28,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Mother?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.52,0:04:50.79,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.41,0:04:53.07,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,This is my son, Asahi.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.46,0:04:55.44,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,We're living separately now.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.73,0:04:57.28,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I see him once a month.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.32,0:05:00.50,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.82,0:05:02.57,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,That's no good.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.86,0:05:08.10,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,You have to bow low like this.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.33,0:05:10.69,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey, Asahi!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.33,0:05:12.56,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that, Miyo-chan!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.79,0:05:15.93,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,He's not used to this kind of thing yet.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.29,0:05:17.42,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes I am!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.34,0:05:30.81,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Things have really changed, haven't they?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.32,0:05:34.76,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I've never seen the captain look that kind.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.48,0:05:39.98,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Would it kill him to be nicer to me too?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.48,0:05:42.81,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,This is simply splendid...
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.81,0:05:43.82,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Listen!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.21,0:05:45.55,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, certainly...
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.74,0:05:47.60,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,He seems to have a different air about him.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.91,0:05:48.72,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.44,0:05:53.21,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,In front of Miyo he's a completely different man.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.36,0:05:55.18,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.20,0:05:59.87,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,To think meeting someone could change a man that much.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.77,0:06:04.71,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Was my introduction earlier incorrect?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.19,0:06:06.65,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Kids will be kids.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.97,0:06:08.08,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Pay it no mind.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.35,0:06:56.10,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Miyo, do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.42,0:06:57.35,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.90,0:06:59.29,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,There's someone I want you to meet.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.59,0:07:00.27,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.77,0:07:01.82,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.12,0:07:10.63,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,How's the party so far?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.28,0:07:12.24,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Are you getting used to it?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.79,0:07:14.60,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, somehow.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.81,0:07:16.59,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,There's no need to be too self-conscious.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.30,0:07:20.79,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,The night breeze will help you relax a bit.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.35,0:07:21.99,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.29,0:07:32.68,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Kiyoka, you came.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.34,0:07:34.68,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.04,0:07:41.05,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Good to see you.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.23,0:07:43.76,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,It's been awhile, Takaihito-sama.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.52,0:07:49.61,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Come, sit with me.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.04,0:07:56.52,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,This must be the Saimori girl, then.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.07,0:07:57.53,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.00,0:08:00.73,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to meet you. My name is Miyo Saimori.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.40,0:08:02.33,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Before you is...
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.33,0:08:04.22,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,The Emperor's second son.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.76,0:08:07.50,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Blessed with the Gift of Divine Revelation, this is Takaihito-sama.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.37,0:08:11.63,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey now...
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.52,0:08:18.63,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I came here today because I wanted to talk to the daughter of the Saimori Clan...
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.97,0:08:23.56,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,...and to explain the disturbances at the Royal Burial Grounds.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.04,0:08:26.11,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I am truly sorry to have inconvenienced you.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.59,0:08:28.72,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,The Usuba Clan, the Saimori Clan...
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.21,0:08:32.67,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,They all had their lives disrupted by my father.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.22,0:08:35.68,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,What in the world is this about?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.68,0:08:39.19,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,All of it was orchestrated by the Emperor.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.71,0:08:43.06,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Truly pathetic, but it is what it is.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.69,0:08:45.13,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Why would he do such a thing?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.70,0:08:49.92,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,My father was particularly afraid of Dream Sight.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.53,0:08:53.72,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,The strength of this Gift depends on its user.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.93,0:08:57.71,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,It is said that Dream Sight surpasses even the power of Divine Revelation.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.36,0:09:02.09,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Nonetheless, if there were no Dream Sight user...
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.09,0:09:04.70,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,The Usuba clan would pose no threat.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.00,0:09:11.31,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,However, Sumi Usuba was born with the Gift of Telepathy.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.56,0:09:15.43,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,With this, the possibility of a Dream Sight user being born came to pass.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.61,0:09:22.95,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,My father believed the purer the blood of the Usuba, the likelier a gifted birth.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.39,0:09:27.89,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,He moved to block Sumi's marriage in the Usuba clan.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.47,0:09:31.88,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,He worked from behind the scenes.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.40,0:09:34.40,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,He pulled the strings of the Tsurugi Trading Company in his favor.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.69,0:09:36.64,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,The Usuba Clan grew weak.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.71,0:09:43.25,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,At the same time, being unable to produce any gift users,
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.62,0:09:45.90,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,the Saimori clan was in decline.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.06,0:09:51.28,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Baiting them with money and the unique ability of the Usuba, he married Sumi off to the Saimori Clan.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.62,0:09:55.20,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,He succeeded in separating her from the Usuba Clan.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.16,0:09:58.91,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,And then, into the Saimori Clan,
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.23,0:10:01.60,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,a daughter was born. You.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.43,0:10:04.64,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.12,0:10:09.75,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,The head of the Saimori Clan apologized when he learned you did not manifest a gift.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.04,0:10:14.13,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,After that revelation, he married you off to Kudou.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.59,0:10:16.80,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,That changed everything.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.49,0:10:19.04,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I think I have a handle on it.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.38,0:10:22.34,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Once Miyo was released from the Saimori Clan, the seal was broken.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.65,0:10:25.61,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,His Majesty must have discovered Miyo had awakened her Gift.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.90,0:10:29.90,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,So we were the targets of the Royal Burial Ground incident?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.76,0:10:32.44,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.46,0:10:37.40,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, with your engagement set in stone,
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.58,0:10:40.99,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,you posed an even greater threat to my father.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.48,0:10:44.52,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,It was to keep us apart.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.19,0:10:50.88,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,However, there's another reason my father went to such great lengths...
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.60,0:10:54.26,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Keep this between us.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.98,0:11:01.27,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,The emperor has already lost the Gift of Divine Revelation.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.38,0:11:05.00,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,He must've been under immense pressure.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.53,0:11:08.56,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Abandoning all his political machinations.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.03,0:11:10.53,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Exhuming the Royal Burial Grounds.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.80,0:11:14.89,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Drawing everyone into his plan, he wanted you gone.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.30,0:11:19.40,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,It makes my blood boil.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.28,0:11:26.10,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,My father needlessly sacrificed the lives of innocents for his own convenience.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.23,0:11:30.82,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Both Saimori and Usuba, forced to cooperate, became victims.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.87,0:11:35.28,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,All because of my father's selfishness.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.55,0:11:40.16,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,So then the Usubas won't be charged with a crime?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.26,0:11:43.13,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.50,0:11:48.29,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Your life has changed a lot because of my father.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.23,0:11:53.03,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I am truly sorry.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.45,0:11:59.35,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Despite that, I was able to meet Kiyoka-sama.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.13,0:12:03.09,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,In this moment, I am truly blessed.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.05,0:12:08.86,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.96,0:12:10.48,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.68,0:12:15.86,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm glad we got to chat this evening.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.39,0:12:17.40,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll see you soon.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.76,0:12:19.39,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.77,0:12:35.21,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I never thought you'd be able to talk with Taikaihito-sama so openly.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.59,0:12:37.73,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,You were genuine.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.41,0:12:40.98,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.26,0:13:33.16,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.58,0:13:34.57,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.12,0:13:42.99,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,My word, that child...
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.20,0:13:44.60,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Miyo-chan, I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.91,0:13:46.71,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.52,0:13:50.88,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Alright, crisis averted.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.13,0:13:56.98,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Asahi!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.07,0:13:58.98,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.29,0:14:02.78,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,That's right, I never introduced you.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.58,0:14:05.87,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,This is my ex-husband.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.13,0:14:08.42,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,And now you know.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.03,0:14:10.00,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.34,0:14:12.18,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I've been out of contact.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.38,0:14:14.71,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I've been busy too, so we're even.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.06,0:14:16.05,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey, Asahi!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.20,0:14:16.87,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.45,0:14:23.79,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,You've been in a bad mood all day.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.06,0:14:24.86,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.32,0:14:29.23,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,When he met Miyo, he was acting strange.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.55,0:14:35.67,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Asahi, what's the most important thing to remember when meeting someone for the first time?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.23,0:14:37.04,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,To smile.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.35,0:14:38.09,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.37,0:14:41.41,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,So if you're always sulking like that,
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.41,0:14:43.30,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Miyo-chan's not going to like you!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.60,0:14:44.99,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,That's fine, I mean...
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.30,0:14:48.41,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I hate Miyo-san anyway!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.13,0:14:54.04,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Miyo-san stole mom. That's why I hate her!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.40,0:14:58.12,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.73,0:15:04.09,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,The truth is Hazuki and I see each other once a month.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.47,0:15:08.43,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Recently, Hazuki has been talking a lot about Miyo-san.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.80,0:15:11.70,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,It seems like Asahi didn't like that.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.11,0:15:17.19,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I never thought it would lead to something like this.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.77,0:15:20.11,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,He was just jealous of Miyo-chan.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.41,0:15:24.94,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,My little goofball.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.15,0:15:27.82,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,This is how much I love my Asahi.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.49,0:15:32.20,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Then who do you love more, Miyo or me?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.05,0:15:35.02,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Do you love your father?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.08,0:15:36.78,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I love him.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.44,0:15:38.58,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Do you love me?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.01,0:15:39.91,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Lots!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.38,0:15:42.84,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Then who do you love more, your father or me?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.57,0:15:50.73,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,You will always have a special place in my heart, Asahi.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.92,0:15:54.23,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,But, Miyo-chan is very important to me, too.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.67,0:15:57.97,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,You both are family to me.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.31,0:16:02.20,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Miyo-san is family, too?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.64,0:16:03.95,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.29,0:16:07.98,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Even though we live apart, we're still family.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.51,0:16:11.07,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Miyo-chan may not be related by blood,
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.44,0:16:13.32,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,but I'm so proud of my little sister.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.36,0:16:18.19,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.76,0:16:21.01,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Hazuki-san...
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.59,0:16:23.49,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.91,0:16:26.03,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm proud of my sister, too.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.93,0:16:29.82,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.07,0:16:32.89,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's it!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.06,0:16:37.24,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you! That's what I'm talking about!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.00,0:16:40.39,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,That's why, Asahi.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.96,0:16:42.90,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Please be kind to Miyo-chan.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.42,0:16:48.19,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.04,0:16:52.03,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I ruined your dress.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.94,0:16:58.21,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.21,0:17:01.37,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,It's so precious you were jealous of Miyo-chan.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.37,0:17:03.91,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Too tight, mom!
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.33,0:17:06.29,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.53,0:17:12.23,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Just as family can take on many forms,
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.83,0:17:16.71,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,so too can happiness.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.39,0:17:24.38,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Even now, somewhere, true happiness is being born.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.26,0:17:32.84,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Surely, the future will deliver this happiness.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.72,0:17:40.03,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Our happiness.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.08,0:17:46.57,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I've been able to convey this to Miyo.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.22,0:17:53.21,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Could she sense it?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.31,0:18:00.06,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Even just a little bit?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.32,0:18:09.46,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Together, we'll discover a new happiness.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.25,0:18:11.88,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Miyo.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.79,0:18:22.37,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.89,0:18:26.03,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Whoops!
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.32,0:18:27.57,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.10,0:18:32.62,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,H-here...
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.43,0:18:34.70,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.27,0:18:38.45,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,So, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.94,0:18:40.67,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Pardon the intrusion.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.03,0:18:44.21,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm just here to make a proposal.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.07,0:18:48.43,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Would you like to hire me as Miyo's bodyguard?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.62,0:18:50.40,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.73,0:18:52.25,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,From now on,
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.58,0:18:55.80,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Miyo will have to deal with the Gift of Dream Sight.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.35,0:18:59.97,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,If only there were someone else who could protect her...
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.24,0:19:01.78,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,It could come in handy.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.99,0:19:05.27,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I was wondering what you were getting at.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.67,0:19:07.43,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I have to leave for work.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.79,0:19:09.02,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Miyo-chan!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.36,0:19:10.33,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Kiyoka!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.66,0:19:11.77,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm coming in!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.06,0:19:13.49,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,What is it this time?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.35,0:19:18.05,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Miyo-sama.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.47,0:19:21.07,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Yurie-san.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.62,0:19:23.24,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,It's just Yurie.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.47,0:19:26.01,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Hazuki, too? Why?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.38,0:19:27.56,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,A-ha...
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.91,0:19:29.48,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,What's up with you?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.68,0:19:30.89,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,It's been awhile.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.47,0:19:35.31,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Actually I'm just here to deliver a proposal to Kudou-san.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.74,0:19:39.83,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm inquiring about becoming Miyo's bodyguard.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.16,0:19:42.34,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,That's reassuring.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.77,0:19:45.09,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,They should be pleased!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.20,0:19:46.33,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.60,0:19:51.10,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm worn out from this morning.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.40,0:19:53.37,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Kiyoka-sama.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.28,0:19:56.09,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Your hair tie is loose.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.68,0:19:57.96,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Let me tie it for you.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.07,0:19:59.09,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Bend down, please.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.48,0:20:00.91,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Sorry, please go ahead.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.34,0:20:06.43,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,All done.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.65,0:20:08.73,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Kiyoka-sama.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.75,0:20:13.13,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Um, could you please bend down once more?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.16,0:20:15.36,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.12,0:20:26.25,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I hope you do your best and work hard today.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.21,0:20:28.07,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Miyo...
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.73,0:20:29.41,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.70,0:20:31.83,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Why are you doing that?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.87,0:20:35.80,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.45,0:20:40.98,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I thought it might cheer you up.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.26,0:20:43.47,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,You didn't like it?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.13,0:20:45.14,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.35,0:20:46.49,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.21,0:21:02.40,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,It made me feel better.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.05,0:21:04.75,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm off.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.24,0:21:25.65,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Have a good day!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.16,0:21:29.57,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,As for the happy times...
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.03,0:21:32.08,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,In the blink of an eye,
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.40,0:21:33.40,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,before you know it,
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.59,0:21:37.18,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Summer has already turned to fall.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.12,0:21:41.54,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,Kiyoka-sama has given me a new perspective...
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.96,0:21:46.16,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,For the first time, I am able to see true happiness.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.61,0:21:50.48,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,It is my precious treasure.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.53,0:21:52.42,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,From now on...
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.84,0:21:56.11,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I want to weave a tale together.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.29,0:21:58.66,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,To walk together.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.31,0:22:03.11,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm absolutely sure...
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.01,0:22:08.19,Dial-ENG,,0,0,0,,...it will be my true happiness.
